{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1244441, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "要做学术1，要找工作2", "timestamp": 1615536326, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244444, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1", "timestamp": 1615536337, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244460, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "个人喜欢1", "timestamp": 1615536482, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244462, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 同意Alice", "timestamp": 1615536488, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244465, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 但是博士有硬性毕业要求…2如果玩脱了容易翻车（延毕）", "timestamp": 1615536512, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244477, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我原来老板是1，感觉很舒服，我每次讨论都能很快找到人，然后思路一卡住交流下就能解决\n现在老板是2，感觉就摸鱼没啥大事，但是遇到困难我一个大四学生就得全靠自己解决。。感觉难度挺大的\n可能是我比较卷吧", "timestamp": 1615536686, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244481, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得既然是博士，无论如何不要选2；做学术选1，工作的话，可以找一个已经长聘的压力不那么大，但也不完全放养的导师（中庸之道）。", "timestamp": 1615536756, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244487, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 如果硕士想都别想直接选2，然后自己实习三年，出去比被push导师拉着干活的好多了", "timestamp": 1615536823, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244555, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1", "timestamp": 1615537368, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244567, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢大家！dz是shhc的......dz心里也更喜欢1 ，但1 的老师目前不要dz，可能自己实力不够。所以在犹豫要不要争取一把", "timestamp": 1615537516, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244573, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz给的信息不够多啊，push是指鼓励你尽可能多的出成果还是只要工作量达不到要求就破口大骂？年轻导师的学术能力如何，是真正可以给你指导还是胡乱开一些不切实际的脑洞并且要求你必须照做？身边有不少朋友选了1然后后悔的，如果选2自觉一点并且多和同学讨论效果不一定就会差，dz还是要好好考虑一下啊", "timestamp": 1615537642, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244627, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: Grace说的很对。确实不能够这样简单来概括。dz觉得1学术上可以给指导，就是工作量饱和，玩的时间少。师兄师姐很好氛围也很好。2的话学术一般，就是放养没那么大压力，但学到的东西有限。师兄师姐也不错。", "timestamp": 1615538269, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244633, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: dz是喜欢玩的，但1可以给学术上的安心感。鱼和熊掌不能兼得，非常纠结", "timestamp": 1615538309, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244636, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "3.基本上能拿到tenure，组内建制稳定产出，处于push和不push叠加态的中年老板", "timestamp": 1615538320, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244771, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "2 挺好的，自己水几篇文章，到毕业前一年找份实习，然后转正或校招", "timestamp": 1615539530, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244775, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 我找找看吧！现在处于选导末期很难了。谢谢！", "timestamp": 1615539553, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244779, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 生物很难水文章，实习也难吧", "timestamp": 1615539598, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244790, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大导师院士2，小导师1，感觉不错", "timestamp": 1615539705, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244817, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 2无title", "timestamp": 1615540039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1244941, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 生物还是慎选1吧", "timestamp": 1615541722, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245034, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 唉", "timestamp": 1615542669, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245145, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "做学术也可以选2，特别是2对于科研独立性的培养，这是你以后做教职很重要的能力。", "timestamp": 1615543911, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245151, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然前提是你自律有motivation可以保证产出。", "timestamp": 1615543957, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245153, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 1", "timestamp": 1615543964, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245163, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "另一点是，一些个人的大创新（运气好的话）在2的条件下更容易实现", "timestamp": 1615544026, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245294, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1.5", "timestamp": 1615545653, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245327, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 2很难", "timestamp": 1615546036, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245343, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz目前是3的老板，也想看看大家的想法", "timestamp": 1615546133, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245763, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 2难所以对于你能力的提升大啊，1固然产出多可以帮你找到教职，但很容易后劲不足，独立性缺乏。", "timestamp": 1615549910, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245805, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得最好的情况是，老师学术水平高，可以给予你有效指导，且放养，且身边有好的学术环境。\n如果这几条都满足且你自律有行动力的话，应该是最好的结果了。\n如果这几条有一些不满足，那可能1确实会好于2。", "timestamp": 1615550223, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1245904, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz的放养是什么意思呢？\n我理解的是可以在你需要的时候给你提供资源或者指导，但是基本不对你的进度做出要求（不push）。", "timestamp": 1615551204, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1246703, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 2可能没有那么多资源吧，也并非大牛", "timestamp": 1615558243, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1247006, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz是2，天天摸鱼", "timestamp": 1615561515, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1247453, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 某些放养是可能你1个月都见不到导师……", "timestamp": 1615565368, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1247554, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 这种确实过分。。。但我知道有的老师是我所说的那种放养的", "timestamp": 1615566252, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1247794, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "只要1是一个愿意跟学生沟通的导师，不是一个一点就着的脾气，那就选1吧。。研究生已经是打工人了，还是尽早认清这一点吧，出活最重要。而且在清华的年轻老师关系网也都经营的挺好的（听说新老师进来的话需要系里其他教授全员通过", "timestamp": 1615568826, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1248403, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Olivia: 唉确实。研究生打工人石锤。好难呀", "timestamp": 1615598440, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1248549, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 想开点嘛，读研究生都二十好几的人了，之前已经被家庭和社会包养了二十多年了哈哈哈哈，打工人才是常态", "timestamp": 1615600986, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1249652, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 245349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Olivia: 哈哈是，谢谢olivia！", "timestamp": 1615612952, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 19, "pid": 245349, "reply": 39, "tag": null, "text": "博士导师选择：\n年轻有为但push几乎没有休息时间的老师扣1\n长聘快退休放养指导少但更多自由支配时间的老师扣2\n呜呜dz好纠结啊", "timestamp": 1615536298, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1615612952, "url": "", "vote": {}}}